message.body: Hey, bb... Kevin's friends are visiting so I'm having dinner with them now. What are you up to?
None plans. Let me know if you get into something good. :) and hey! Hung out with Luke last night...
Freakishly well. Confusing feelings. But good closure. And a new beginning. This reads like a poorly written greeting card
Oh. I'm so so glad!!! I feel like that kind of amiable rendezvous doesn't happen in real life...
Haha. I'm sure his new beard isn't nearly as cute as you are.
